{"id":1185,"date":"2018-08-02T15:18:24","date_gmt":"2018-08-02T19:18:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1185"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:50","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:50","slug":"catherine-grech","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/catherine-grech\/","title":{"rendered":"Catherine Grech"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Catherine Grech enseigne au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent depuis 2007. Elle a obtenu un doctorat de l\u2019Universit\u00e9 McGill en 2010. Dans son m\u00e9moire et dans sa th\u00e8se, elle s\u2019est int\u00e9ress\u00e9e aux repr\u00e9sentations culturelles de la vieillesse. L\u2019\u00e9criture au f\u00e9minin ainsi que l\u2019\u00e9criture autobiographique sont les autres champs d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat auxquels elle a consacr\u00e9 des articles et des communications. La r\u00e9ussite des \u00e9tudiants et \u00e9tudiantes en difficult\u00e9 et des gar\u00e7ons lui tient particuli\u00e8rement \u00e0 c\u0153ur.<\/p>\n<p>Citations pr\u00e9f\u00e9r\u00e9es :<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"litterature\"><p>It is so silent all around that a moment ago when a single wave broke I was startled by its gentle roar.<\/p>\n<p>May Sarton,\u00a0<em>The House by the Sea<\/em>, 1977<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"litterature\"><p>Ce qu\u2019on peut aimer \u00e0 Alger, c\u2019est ce dont tout le monde vit: la mer au tournant de chaque rue, un certain poids de soleil, la beaut\u00e9 de la race.<\/p>\n<p>Albert Camus,\u00a0<em>Noces. L\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e0 Alger<\/em>, 1938<\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[214],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1185","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-francais"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1185","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1185"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1185"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1185"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1185"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1185"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}